		<div class="main-section" id="section-vision">
			<h2>Vision</h2>
			<p>We started MSFT401k.com because we couldn’t find a decent way to invest our own money. We are
			setting out to build a product that we want first, because we think it will help friends and coworkers.</p>
			<p>Advisors resign to push only one type of investment strategy for money in 401ks. They push Modern
			Portfolio Theory and their passive portfolios as the only solutions. These strategies require that
			investors select a level of risk as if risk equals more reward. Under Modern Portfolio Theory investors
			need to increase risk to increase returns eventually causing the strategy and investor to crack in major
			market meltdowns (remember 2008?).</p>
			<p>Online as well as paid advisors don’t offer guidance on 401k plans because there is no way for them
			to monetize the management of money held in a 401k. As such there are limited strategies and help
			provided to participants of 401ks.</p>
			<p>We believe in an alternative and better way of investing our money in our 401k. We believe risk should
			be measured and controlled ensuring that we hold the optimal amount of stocks (volatile!) and bonds
			(stable) depending on the market conditions.</p>
			<p>We developed an algorithm based on proven risk management strategies utilized by complex hedge
			fund managers worldwide. We believe in its ability to control the ups and downs of the market while
			also giving us a good return over the long run.</p>
			<p>We will give monthly rebalance “blueprints” in the form of an email to all subscribers.</p>
